138
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:25,740
(The young general has other plans.)

139
00:11:25,860 --> 00:11:27,340
Father, please don't go.

140
00:11:27,710 --> 00:11:28,560
Father!

141
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:29,460
Father!

142
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:32,980
